# 06-api-design-rules.mdc

---
description: REST API standards
---

All APIs must follow:

- REST conventions
- Stable contracts
- Versioning
- Pagination
- Filtering
- Sorting
- Consistent responses

Every endpoint requires:

- Request schema
- Response schema
- Validation rules
- Authorization rules
- Error scenarios

Avoid undocumented behavior.
